&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Testing Roadmap:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with paid media marketers to build, execute, and scale a structured creative testing matrix—experimenting with diverse hooks, treatments, and variants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Measurement &amp;amp; Iteration:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively review paid media performance data to identify trends, analyze creative wins/losses (tracking metrics like Hook Rate and CTR), and rapidly iterate on winning variants.&lt;/li&gt;
