&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empower:&lt;/strong&gt; Design scalable, self-serve dashboards (Looker/Tableau) that help your teammates make faster, smarter decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead efforts to streamline data collection and translate complex business needs into clear data products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experiment:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with Product and Marketing to run A/B tests that directly influence our user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
