&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; An ability to see both the granular details and the &quot;big picture&quot; of a luxury marketplace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Spirit:&lt;/strong&gt; You thrive when &lt;strong&gt;succeeding together&lt;/strong&gt; and can succinctly exchange ideas with both technical and non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; A degree in a quantitative field (Statistics, Math, Econ, Business) or equivalent practical experience&lt;/li&gt;
